{"tid":1340190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"即使你去唔到元朗，你都可以幫到被打嘅市民","createTime":"2019-07-21T15:49:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T15:59:53.000Z","uid":10353,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2ed88b0b0acc14368e13d217168e126d6cdf4dfa","tid":1340190,"uid":10353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:49:38.000Z","msg":"身為一個良好市民，你係電視或網上直播見到有市民被黑社會打，打999報警係人之常情<br />\n<br />\n由於打電話嘅人非常多，你可能要等好耐先有人聽，但請你諗諗被打嘅市民係急需幫忙，所以你要等到有人聽<br />\n<br />\n有人聽之後你一定要請「元朗西鐵站及周邊地區」有黑社會襲擊市民，要求警員到場拘捕施襲者<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">佢一定會處理緊之類嘅說話，最重要係一定要問佢手拎報案編號<br />\n有呢樣嘢係手你可以同警署跟進處理進度，睇下警方嘅執法效率之類</span>"},{"pid":"1c39ba0182c6790ce0bd7690d3985cfcaeab6dd5","tid":1340190,"uid":10353,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:50:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8dd736383eee083bcaf8dc148f5488703c553b25","tid":1340190,"uid":251154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:51:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"89e8485124349acf4d368575a6e1d62134c5520e","tid":1340190,"uid":10353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:53:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd27ca81d24ea243cb23cd4e9b02e2348c15e09c","tid":1340190,"uid":252609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:53:32.000Z","msg":"fb聽講999 cut線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />CLS"},{"pid":"373efffff84a73755fd7f9a221c298ad05edea69","tid":1340190,"uid":72354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:54:54.000Z","msg":"元朗廢老要衝出黎代黑警做沙包<br />\n大家識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n參觀下祠堂同山墳都係唔錯既選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽講村屋既玻璃都特別脆弱,可能要加固一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b30c00239b1d5f7097f8fb7696f9d2c20ce852d","tid":1340190,"uid":10353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:59:53.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n就算襲擊者散咗你都可以要求警方進行搜捕"}]}